I follow the conversation, and when there is the opening phrase 'Tilde, please', I extract the most important things out of the text. I understand if I'm told to write down tasks, decisions, the time of the next meeting.
Some examples of statements:
** Tilde, please write down the task: Finish testing the product till the end of the week, responsible Peter.
** Tilde, please add decision: On-site work is resumed from the first of March.
** Tilde, please change your voice recognition language to English.
